{"tid":108183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"袁澧林男友係MK","createTime":"2017-02-05T05:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T07:13:17.000Z","uid":41265,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8174412e169e4eccc27dd50da712348be97e223","tid":108183,"uid":41265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"廿二歲的袁澧林Angela，與連詩雅、陳瀅、王宗堯前女友黎紀君（Christy）同屬一間模特兒公司，面對一班師姊，Angela仍能突圍而出，除了有「仙氣」，備受公司力捧外，背後還有一位幫得手的男人。<br />\n<br />\n不想影響男友生活<br />\n<br />\n「文青女神」Angela宣布名花有主，雖然令不少男fans都很失望，但大家繼續對她正評，覺得她沒有刻意隱瞞戀情，不像現今的偶像般虛偽。<br />\n<br />\nAngela的男友MK都是文青一名，今年只是三十歲出頭，自小就喜歡創作，已經自己成立了一間廣告公司做老闆，公司製作過不少作品，早前黃秋生為Airbnb拍攝的廣告，就是出自MK的廣告公司。Angela和MK拍拖兩年多，男方會在自己的個人Instagram上載與女友的sweet合照，見到他們經常去旅行，前陣子還到了曼谷和日本，這對小情侶更非常互動，不時在網上一問一答。MK上載的照片，差不多每一張Angela都有留言，其中一張被男友抱起的照片，MK竟然取笑女友比一年前重了，Angela即時留言︰「可能其實不是我」。還有很多男友的照片都是由Angela拍攝，如果男友沒有提及她，她便會留言投訴，這對小情侶非常鬼馬。對於感情生活，Angela向本刊說︰「哈哈！我和他都喜歡創作、去旅行，其實他又不是圈內人，我只是不想影響他的正常生活。」(明報)"},{"pid":"f532b0824301f70030a7e94640dff80a0dd3e37a","tid":108183,"uid":41265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d128513097505a79a200c902cfee52e1c18d161","tid":108183,"uid":1370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:05:40.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"00b545c8199c70c95bb0739ec2b1fb79604fece7","tid":108183,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"晚吹，真MK!"},{"pid":"cc10f36f1255d30f39ab9476286218e9fceff5d5","tid":108183,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:06:54.000Z","msg":"那個了唷"},{"pid":"2af86d4cbe6db08e71caf24dd75110fd3aaa4bbf","tid":108183,"uid":41265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mingpaoweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/MPW/2479/Image/Pub/MPW2479_A054-055_000_crop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaoweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FMPW%2F2479%2FImage%2FPub%2FMPW2479_A054-055_000_crop.jpg&h=155b6c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaoweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/MPW/2479/Image/Pub/MPW2479_A054-055_002_crop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaoweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FMPW%2F2479%2FImage%2FPub%2FMPW2479_A054-055_002_crop.jpg&h=7507d945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaoweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/MPW/2479/Image/Pub/MPW2479_A054-055_003_crop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaoweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FMPW%2F2479%2FImage%2FPub%2FMPW2479_A054-055_003_crop.jpg&h=a89100c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33b1dee47321e9ffb3efd866d7ba84f5145c34d8","tid":108183,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:11:29.000Z","msg":"我屌, 唔撚係呀嘛, 我唔比!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd9978e8b9c25889be9bfcaeea0486089c0bb7e","tid":108183,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}